OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDrought prompts French ban 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fon garden swimming pools   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Garden swimming pools are to be banned 
OL,6, from sale in a part of southern France 
OL,7, over worsening water shortages.        
OL,9,FFrance's Ecological Transition Minister
OL,10,FChristophe Bechu said that             
OL,11,FPyrenees-Orientales, which borders     
OL,12,FSpanish Catalonia, will be officially  
OL,13,Fdeclared at drought "crisis" level from
OL,14,F10 May.                                
OL,16,FBans on car-washing, garden-watering   
OL,17,Fand pool-filling will also kick in from
OL,18,Fthe same date.                         
OL,20,F"We need to get out of our culture of  
OL,21,Fabundance," said Mr Bechu.             
